{"tid":2099140,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"廉署貪污問題諮詢委員會工作報告　貪污情況維持低水平","createTime":"2020-07-08T04:22:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T04:46:11.000Z","uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b55cbd95d93e0de84725610f4b4b41095af5cae6","tid":2099140,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T04:22:42.000Z","msg":"廉署貪污問題諮詢委員會主席廖長江在立法會大會，就委員會2019年工作報告發言，表示去年香港貪污情況維持低水平，周年民調中有98.1%受訪者表示，過去12個月沒有親身遇到貪污。<br />\n<br />\n廖長江說，廉署去年接獲2297宗與選舉無關的投訴，比前年下降14%，另外接獲623宗涉嫌違反《選舉（舞弊及非法行為）條例》的投訴，當中518宗涉及區議會選舉。他說，廉署主動與政制及內地事務局聯絡，檢討選舉程序及提供防貪建議，確保未來選舉廉潔公平。<br />\n<br />\n全文: <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536502-20200708.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536502-20200708.htm&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDKzyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=1f47d460\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536502-20200708.htm&h=387fa436\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536502-20200708.htm</a>"},{"pid":"410fac451c5bac32fa654baf6464176ffde3a55e","tid":2099140,"uid":198343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T04:23:25.000Z","msg":"未執笠咩?"},{"pid":"fccc1adb00e04393f5420a639366d9cec0e925f4","tid":2099140,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T04:23:55.000Z","msg":"ICAC Cafe: 我轉行賣咖啡"},{"pid":"4fff55c570aebc109e8e8be0da5bd8c0a76e3cec","tid":2099140,"uid":300006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T04:24:13.000Z","msg":"貪污公署"},{"pid":"ec2799719a769e088a261323d38a42bc8018f5c3","tid":2099140,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fccc1adb00e04393f5420a639366d9cec0e925f4","tid":2099140,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T04:23:55.000Z","msg":"ICAC Cafe: 我轉行賣咖啡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T04:26:37.000Z","msg":"改做單